style
  hr{margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:15px}
  h4{margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:5px}
#wrapper
  #mods
    header#page-title(style="margin-bottom:20px")
      .container
        h1 D2Moddin Invites
        ul.breadcrumb
          li
            a(href='/') Home
          li.active Queue
    section.container
      .row
        .col-md-9
          .row
            .col-sm-4.col-md-4
              h3 Beta Queue
              hr
              h1(style="text-align:center") {{queue.totalCount|number}}
              p(style="width:100%;text-align:center")
                | Total Players
              h1(ng-if="queue.inQueue&&auth.isAuthed",style="text-align:center") {{queue.originalPos|number}}
              p(ng-if="queue.inQueue&&auth.isAuthed",style="width:100%;text-align:center")
                | Original Queue Position
              h1(ng-if="queue.inQueue&&auth.isAuthed&&!queue.invited",style="text-align:center") {{queue.myPos|number}}
              p(ng-if="queue.inQueue&&auth.isAuthed&&!queue.invited",style="width:100%;text-align:center")
                | Position in Queue
              h1(ng-if="queue.inQueue&&queue.invited",style="text-align:center") Invited
              p
              a.btn.btn-success(href="/lobbies",style="width:100%",ng-if="auth.isAuthed&&queue.invited") Start Playing
              button.btn.btn-success(style="width:100%",ng-if="!queue.inQueue&&auth.isAuthed",ng-click="queue.joinQueue()") Join the Queue
              a.btn.btn-success(href="http://fundrazr.com/campaigns/2nfla/pay?perk=36yD7",style="width:100%",ng-if="auth.isAuthed&&queue.inQueue&&!queue.invited") Skip the Queue
              button.btn.btn-success(ng-click="startEnterKey()",style="width:100%",ng-if="auth.isAuthed&&queue.inQueue&&!queue.invited") Use Invite Key
              button.btn.btn-success(ng-click="startSignin()",style="width:100%",ng-if="!auth.isAuthed") Signin w/ Steam
            .col-sm-8.col-md-8
              .desc
                h4 IMPORTANT: GETTING AN INVITE
                hr
                p 
                  | You can donate to support the project and skip the queue! The
                  | first perk is at $2.50 and awards you an invite code
                  | for D2Moddin.
                p
                  b PLEASE NOTE that we send out invites TWICE A DAY  
                  | and that you must include your steam ID in the information form after the donation to prevent additional delays processing your donation.
                h3.page-header(style="margin:10px 0 10px") What is D2Moddin 
                p
                  b Dota 2 
                  | is a 2013 multiplayer online battle arena video game
                  | and the stand-alone sequel to the Defense of the Ancients
                  | (DotA) mod.
                p
                  b D2Moddin 
                  | is an effort to return to the roots of Dota 2 as a
                  | mod, allowing thousands of players to easily play unofficial
                  | custom game modes created by the community.
                p
                  | Thousands of games are now hosted daily on D2Moddin's server
                  | network, and with a queue of over 201,000 players, we are
                  | constantly working to scale up our service and allow more
                h4 The Game Modes
                hr
                p 
                  | Currently we host four game modes on D2Moddin (and are
                  | adding more as they are completed):
                p 
                  b Reflex (by BMD)
                  | - a fast paced action game that excercises
                  | hand-eye coordination and fast reflexes.
                p
                  b Hero Line Wars (by EinAlex)
                  | - Fight against creeps sent by
                  | the other team and send waves to quickly overwhelm the enemy
                  | and increase your periodic income!
                p
                  b Pudge Wars (by Kobb and Aderum) 
                  |  - The classic WC3 mod
                  | re-created in Dota 2.
                p
                  b Fight or Flight
                  |  (by MoD)  
                  | - The first competitive Dota 2 mod.
        aside.col-md-3
          h3 Donations
          hr
          .fr-widget(data-type="badge",data-variant="tall",data-width="220",data-url="http://fnd.us/c/2nfla")
script(type="text/javascript",src="//static.fundrazr.com/widgets/1957/widgets.js")
